What:		/sys/devices/platform/exynos-drm/<panel>/error_count_te
Date:		March, 2023
KernelVersion:	5.15
Contact:	"Jeremy DeHaan" <jdehaan@google.com>
Description:
		This file provides the count of all TE errors detected during
		runtime.

		Valid panels are 'primary-panel' or 'secondary-panel'.

